<p><img style="width: 813px; height: 213px;" src="/media/13089493/our-holidays-838x220.jpg?width=813&amp;height=213&amp;mode=max" alt="summer holidays" data-udi="umb://media/b40cf9d23b4a4012aaed9b15dfdb0eab" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ With over 85 years of experience you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ You'll have the reassurance and expert guidance of our reps when in resort. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ <strong>New for 2023:</strong> enjoy two guided walks per week in selected resorts*.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️Flights from your choice of 15 regional airports, transfers and accommodation are included in your holiday.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c9869bf0e4e9431d98d0277c1db49284}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">View 2023 holiday Deals</a></div>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/3471b74e93f54f109e136e4d91626d89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3471b74e93f54f109e136e4d91626d89}" title="Best Value Summer Holidays 2024" class="c-btn">View 2024 holiday Deals</a></p>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Looking for more inspiration?</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">Take a walking holiday with us. We offer options for every type of walker, including relaxing resorts, destinations for foodies, surprise-filled resorts and awe-inspiring views.</p>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a}" title="Appetising walking holidays">Appetising</a></h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8f01b61468784dcaa43c28a175d0b07a}" title="Appetising walking holidays"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094131/summer-appetisizing-501x300.jpg?width=500&amp;height=299.4011976047904" alt="appetising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/87d041ea3e06407ba628212066cd996d" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb}" title="Surprising walking holidays">Surprising</a></h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2345192f0fb94242b7572aa227f073bb}" title="Surprising walking holidays"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094134/summer-suprising-501x300.jpg?width=500&amp;height=299.4011976047904" alt="surprising walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/86e74142f0c1406e8dae086ff4a4bf9a" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/75bc0c6f88e04aa08720a6f84ad48c94" href="/{localLink:umb://document/75bc0c6f88e04aa08720a6f84ad48c94}" title="Rewarding walking holidays">Rewarding</a></h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/75bc0c6f88e04aa08720a6f84ad48c94" href="/{localLink:umb://document/75bc0c6f88e04aa08720a6f84ad48c94}" title="Rewarding walking holidays"><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094133/summer-rewarding-501x300.jpg?width=207&amp;height=21" alt="rewarding walking holidays" data-udi="umb://media/a6f285ef9b0f4f66b3def3f47460fb4e" /></a></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">When you choose an Inghams holiday, you can travel with confidence. We’re here to take the stress out of travelling. We’ve put extra measures in place for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img style="width: 916px; height: 231px; float: left;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=916&amp;height=231&amp;mode=max" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: left;">**<span>Up to two guided walks per week are included in the following resorts: </span><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/mayrhofen" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/saalbach-hinterglemm" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/morzine" title="Morzine">Morzine</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone" title="Limone">Limone</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"> Selva</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b45a359445114107972cbb2b00be85ae}" title="Champoluc" data-anchor="#">Champoluc</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/de185d9ae756482295e4f069ba3a7aaf}" title="Cervinia">Cervinia</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/grindelwald" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/wengen" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt, </a><a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal">Funchal</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico">Caniço</a><span>. </span><span>All walks are subject to availability of local guides, weather conditions and maximum numbers. Where we cannot confirm your preferred option in resort, we will endeavour to offer an alternative subject to the above conditions. </span></p>
